item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Madonna [First album CD rip]
item.description:
Madonna's debut album has versions with different mixes. I was wondering if anyone has the versions of her fist album.

The original version of the album included a 4:48 version of "Burning Up" with a synth-pop arrangement. On many subsequent pressings, however, a 3:41 version driven by electric guitars takes its place.

The version on streaming is different from the CD
